<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 22:05:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>德国和俄罗斯因乌克兰导弹音频泄露发生争执</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-and-russia-spar-over-a-leaked-audio-on-missiles-for-ukraine-berlin-promises-to-investigate/articleshow/108216041.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108216041.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国政府否认了有关俄罗斯公布德国高级军官泄露的谈话内容暗示柏林正在准备对俄罗斯开战的指控。虽然德国当局没有质疑录音的真实性，但德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，将这些武器运送到乌克兰并不是一种选择。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-and-russia-spar-over-a-leaked-audio-on-missiles-for-ukraine-berlin-promises-to-investigate/articleshow/108216041.cms</guid></item><item><title>苹果在 Spotify 案中被欧盟罚款 20 亿美元，将上诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/apple-hit-with-2-billion-eu-antitrust-fine-in-spotify-case-will-appeal/articleshow/108215933.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108215933.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟委员会因不公平的交易条件以及阻止 Spotify 向用户告知 App Store 之外的支付选项而对苹果公司处以 18.4 亿欧元的罚款。苹果计划对这一决定提出质疑，并寻求解决另一项欧盟反垄断调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 21:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/apple-hit-with-2-billion-eu-antitrust-fine-in-spotify-case-will-appeal/articleshow/108215933.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国立法者投票将堕胎纳入宪法权利</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/french-lawmakers-votes-to-make-abortion-constitutional-right/articleshow/108214688.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214688.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国议会周一投票将堕胎权纳入该国宪法，使其成为第一个在基本法中为终止妊娠提供明确保护的国家。聚集在凡尔赛宫的议会下院和上院轻松获得了这一变革所需的五分之三多数，其中 72 名议员投了反对票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/french-lawmakers-votes-to-make-abortion-constitutional-right/articleshow/108214688.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列罢工导致三名黎巴嫩真主党相关部队救援人员死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-strike-kills-three-lebanese-rescue-workers-from-hezbollah-linked-force/articleshow/108214986.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214986.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列在黎巴嫩南部的一次袭击造成三名真主党紧急救援人员死亡。政府和 Al-Hayaa 救援部队证实了这起杀戮事件，使自 10 月以来在以色列袭击中丧生的紧急救援人员总数达到七人。一月份的另一次罢工导致两名急救人员死亡。这场冲突是2006年战争以来最严重的一次，引发了人们对更大规模对抗的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:40:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-strike-kills-three-lebanese-rescue-workers-from-hezbollah-linked-force/articleshow/108214986.cms</guid></item><item><title>白宫称美国呼吁结束海地暴力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-calls-for-end-to-haiti-violence-white-house-says/articleshow/108215205.cms</link><description>白宫周一表示，美国敦促海地所有行为者停止暴力，并将海地人民放在第一位。白宫发言人约翰·柯比表示，白宫正在密切关注海地局势。周末暴力升级，又有 15,000 人逃离战火，武装人员从海地最大的监狱冲走了数千名囚犯。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-calls-for-end-to-haiti-violence-white-house-says/articleshow/108215205.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普集团前首席财务官承认伪证罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/former-trump-organization-cfo-pleads-guilty-to-perjury/articleshow/108215235.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108215235.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;检察官周一表示，唐纳德·特朗普组织的前财务总监因提供与前总统民事欺诈审判有关的虚假信息而承认作伪证。 76 岁的艾伦·韦塞尔伯格 (Allen Weisselberg) 在 2005 年至 2021 年期间担任前总统特朗普房地产和娱乐集团的首席财务官。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/former-trump-organization-cfo-pleads-guilty-to-perjury/articleshow/108215235.cms</guid></item><item><title>冈比亚议会考虑取消女性生殖器切割禁令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gambian-parliament-mulls-lifting-ban-on-female-genital-mutilation/articleshow/108215312.cms</link><description>冈比亚议会周一开始审查一项备受争议的法案，该法案旨在取消自 2015 年以来生效的女性生殖器切割禁令。几个月来，这个问题在冈比亚人中产生了分歧，数十名示威者聚集在议会内外，寻求取消该禁令。禁令。但一些民间社会团体敦促政府立场坚定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 19:32:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gambian-parliament-mulls-lifting-ban-on-female-genital-mutilation/articleshow/108215312.cms</guid></item><item><title>超过十分之六的美国成年人怀疑拜登第二任期的心理能力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/more-than-6-in-10-us-adults-doubts-bidens-mental-capability-for-second-term/articleshow/108214035.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214035.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近的一项调查显示，越来越多的美国成年人因拜登的年龄而对他有效履行职责的能力产生怀疑。约60%的受访者对拜登的心理能力缺乏信心，较今年早些时候略有上升。即将到来的选举被视为对世界上最艰巨工作的考验，两位候选人都已超过退休年龄。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/more-than-6-in-10-us-adults-doubts-bidens-mental-capability-for-second-term/articleshow/108214035.cms</guid></item><item><title>SC 消除了特朗普入主白宫的巨大障碍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/supreme-court-removes-giant-hurdle-from-trumps-path-to-white-house/articleshow/108214032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108214032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国最高法院一致驳回了州法院的一项裁决，为唐纳德·特朗普的总统竞选扫清了道路。该裁决推翻了有关叛乱的指控，这些指控可能阻止他出现在选票上。法院的裁决巩固了特朗普获得共和党提名的道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:17:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/supreme-court-removes-giant-hurdle-from-trumps-path-to-white-house/articleshow/108214032.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列称联合国巴勒斯坦机构雇佣了“450多名恐怖分子”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-over-450-terrorists-employed-by-un-agency-for-palestinians/articleshow/108214909.cms</link><description>以色列军方周一指责联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构（UNRWA）雇佣了属于哈马斯等组织的“450多名恐怖分子”。一份军方声明称：“根据情报，近东救济工程处还雇用了超过 450 名属于加沙地带恐怖组织（主要是哈马斯）的恐怖分子。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-over-450-terrorists-employed-by-un-agency-for-palestinians/articleshow/108214909.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔总理普拉昌达组建新联盟并重组内阁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/nepal-prime-minister-prachanda-forms-new-alliance-restructures-cabinet/articleshow/108213930.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108213930.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼泊尔总理普拉昌达改组内阁，终止与尼泊尔国会的合作关系。与 KP 夏尔马·奥利领导的尼泊尔共产党（联合马克思列宁主义）结盟。国民议会议长的任命产生分歧。西陶拉和最大的共产主义势力被排除在权力之外。印度的利益可能会受到损害。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/nepal-prime-minister-prachanda-forms-new-alliance-restructures-cabinet/articleshow/108213930.cms</guid></item><item><title>超级星期二，美国多州投票盛宴</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/super-tuesday-americas-multi-state-voting-bonanza/articleshow/108206671.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108206671.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;来自 15 个州和一个领地的美国人正在为“超级星期二”做准备，这是竞选日历中的关键一天，将使唐纳德·特朗普更接近获得共和党总统提名。人们普遍预计现任总统乔·拜登将确保其政党获得连任。民主党将宣布爱荷华州邮寄投票的获胜者。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:39:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/super-tuesday-americas-multi-state-voting-bonanza/articleshow/108206671.cms</guid></item><item><title>MH370失踪10年：马来西亚可能重新搜寻失踪飞机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/10-years-of-mh370s-disappearance-aviation-mystery-missing-malaysia-airlines-plane-renew-search/photostory/108203461.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108203461.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马来西亚可能会重新搜寻 MH370，飞机失踪 10 周年即将来临​</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:47:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/10-years-of-mh370s-disappearance-aviation-mystery-missing-malaysia-airlines-plane-renew-search/photostory/108203461.cms</guid></item><item><title>海地因暴力升级宣布进入紧急状态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/haiti-declares-state-of-emergency-as-violence-escalates/articleshow/108204587.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108204587.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;海地政府于周日宣布进入紧急状态，此前首都发生暴力冲突，一名著名帮派头目试图罢免总理阿里尔·亨利，导致两起越狱事件。 Digicel 董事长 Maarten Boute 表示，由于首都部分地区持续发生街头骚乱，他们的线路受到干扰。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:28:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/haiti-declares-state-of-emergency-as-violence-escalates/articleshow/108204587.cms</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚总理：如果找到令人信服的证据，很高兴重新开始MH370搜索</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/happy-to-reopen-mh370-search-if-compelling-evidence-found-malaysian-pm/articleshow/108202878.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108202878.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马来西亚 MH-370 航班神秘失踪十年后，马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣表示，如果出现“令人信服”的证据，愿意重新启动搜索。澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯对持续的悲痛表示遗憾。交通部长安东尼·洛克（Anthony Loke）收到了 Ocean Infinity 提出的一项无治疗、免费的重新搜索建议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 09:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/happy-to-reopen-mh370-search-if-compelling-evidence-found-malaysian-pm/articleshow/108202878.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿联酋第一座印度教石庙在第一个公共周日吸引了 6.5 万名游客</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/uaes-first-hindu-stone-temple-draws-over-65000-visitors-on-first-public-sunday/articleshow/108197077.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108197077.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿联酋第一座印度教寺庙 BAPS Hindu Mandir 在第一个向公众开放的周日吸引了近 65,000 名朝圣者。游客们对人群管理赞不绝口，并享受了令人惊叹的达显。该寺庙的建筑和文化遗产受到墨西哥游客的赞赏。寺庙的开放代表了不同社区之间的团结和多样性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:36:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/uaes-first-hindu-stone-temple-draws-over-65000-visitors-on-first-public-sunday/articleshow/108197077.cms</guid></item><item><title>4名新宇航员前往国际空间站进行为期6个月的停留</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nasa-astronauts-matthew-dominick-michael-barratt-jeanette-epps-russias-alexander-grebenkin-head-to-iss-6-month-stay/articleshow/108192861.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108192861.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由四名宇航员组成的团队，包括美国宇航局的马修·多米尼克、迈克尔·巴拉特、珍妮特·埃普斯和俄罗斯的亚历山大·格雷本金，正在前往国际空间站的途中，监督两艘新火箭飞船的抵达——波音的星际飞船太空舱和塞拉太空公司的追梦者号。该任务由 SpaceX 和 NASA 从佛罗里达州的 NASA 肯尼迪航天中心发射。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:23:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/nasa-astronauts-matthew-dominick-michael-barratt-jeanette-epps-russias-alexander-grebenkin-head-to-iss-6-month-stay/articleshow/108192861.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾外长敦促中国“停止骚扰我们”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/stop-harassing-us-philippines-foreign-minister-urges-china/articleshow/108193899.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108193899.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾外交部长恩里克·马纳洛呼吁和平解决与中国的海上争端，并敦促北京停止骚扰菲律宾。他寻求国际和地区支持，同时密切关注即将到来的美国大选对美菲关系和地区稳定的潜在影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/stop-harassing-us-philippines-foreign-minister-urges-china/articleshow/108193899.cms</guid></item><item><title>年度政治会议即将开幕，中国经济“备受关注”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-economy-of-great-concern-as-annual-political-meeting-to-kick-off/articleshow/108194029.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108194029.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国一年一度的政治会议周一在北京拉开帷幕，官员们在制定来年计划时表示，疲软的经济和青年失业问题令人“高度关注”。他周日表示，“年轻人，特别是应届毕业生的就业”也是如此，在统计局调整计算方法后，到2023年底，官方统计青年失业率在15%左右。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 04:58:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-economy-of-great-concern-as-annual-political-meeting-to-kick-off/articleshow/108194029.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾外长敦促邻国在南海问题上更加坚定地站在一起</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippine-foreign-minister-urges-neighbours-to-stand-together-more-strongly-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/108190515.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108190515.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾在海牙获胜后，菲律宾外交部长恩里克·马纳洛敦促地区邻国维护南海法治。他强调需要合作而不是对抗以及和平解决争端。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 03:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/philippine-foreign-minister-urges-neighbours-to-stand-together-more-strongly-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/108190515.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>